Author: SheDontCarrie
Text: I am 5’1” female and feel like the supposed weight loss intake of 1200 calories is way too high for me. I feel like these numbers do not consider petite people, and if I ate that amount my weight would go nowhere. These are worries I have so I am more comfortable restricting.

Author: Entemma
Text: Yea, i feel like im so small and uw, and also i dont move around a lot, and am in starvation mode, and have bad genetics etc etc... ... So my tdee most be WAY lower than the calculators tell me (i know this isnt true, just ed thoughts)
